It seems the bad decisions continue. In part 2, I return to the scene of the crime one year after Hannah's and Beth's deaths. And, everything seems to point to this being a bad idea. No power. Seclusion. I have a bad feeling about this. Oh and to top it all off, I miss a high five that might lead to Sam's death. Great!
